Try setting a value higher than windows…

[quote=“blah bah7, post:3, topic:151277”][quote author=nator123123 link=topic=206911.msg1819004#msg1819004 date=1192249421]

regedit : Registry Editor

OMGOMGOMG~!:
change/add values,
change/add names,
change/add integers,
change/add binary data,
change/add strings,
